         Dollen recieves Phobia's transmission.  Who the hell was this bot??
Oh well, he said there were attackers, and he WAS on his side, a predacon,
so, he better go help.  He rushed out the room, and ran into GoldenEye's
room.

         "Hey darlin', looks like we got company, let's move!!" He said,
smiling.
